{"tid":230375,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救救耶撚大行動","createTime":"2017-05-05T10:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T17:48:12.000Z","uid":76769,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aedccd785c5d3e79e4db08b43a8cc528780764ce","tid":230375,"uid":76769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"小弟曾經返過2年教會 曾經信哂耶撚嘅教導<br />\n<br />\n但係見過太多不合常理嘅事 <br />\n<br />\n例如耶撚導師話只要信到十足就可以聽到神既說話,同你祈個禱就乜病都好返,祈個禱長短手就會正常返 等等<br />\n<br />\n但我返咗兩年剩係聽人講過 但乜柒都未經歷過<br />\n<br />\n仲目睹過耶撚導師誤人前途等等嘅事件<br />\n<br />\n覺得越返越唔對路 今日我終於離咗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢度有無離咗教嘅巴絲都想拯救返你地嘅朋友出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得咁樣先可以令到教會失去最大財源同埋支持<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有咩方法可以理性咁將中毒未深嘅耶撚拯救返出嚟？<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2b6e2fa954d40059dd028ab43d8bd9442ccc17","tid":230375,"uid":76769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f8752bf7bdbdf553b0955039005be962a48a5d","tid":230375,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cf0c378be34964a7dd1b7f89998f72b09c2433","tid":230375,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜"},{"pid":"f7c8e0d13923f50392fabf8e40246ea2627a7ce5","tid":230375,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"恭喜樓主回復正常人生,耶撚痾到屎都要話係神嘅恩典,基本生活上所以野都要同恩典掛鉤,好撚可悲"}]}